    <briefdescription>
<para>A base class for javascript classes with callable instances. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The functions <computeroutput>callFunction</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>callConstructor</computeroutput> can be overriden to provide custom handling of the class instance when it&apos;s called as a function or as a constructor (with <computeroutput>new</computeroutput>). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
